              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/22471944/" class="">尼采的锤子</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59289474/" class=" " title="祈尘">祈尘</a>
                (生活庸俗而平淡，是诗之过失。)
              
